Package: esmr
Title: Equivalent Soil Mass Tools for Soil Stocks and Properties
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sebastian", "Villarino", , "sebavillarino@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions to compute fixed-depth and equivalent soil mass
    (ESM) statistics for SOC and other soil properties with
    monotone-spline alignment and no-extrapolation options.
